@node "Wprowadzenie" "Introduction"
@{B}@{FG Highlight}@{BG Shadow} Introduction                                                                 @{FG Text}@{BG Background}@{UB}
@{B}______________________________________________________________________________@{UB}
 With an unhided pleasure I present a completed campaign for the excellent
 game Cannon Fodder. Project has been started four years ago. First plan was
 to make a completly new version of game with new graphics, sounds, texts etc.
 Some of objectives are reached partially, some completly not. I hope that our
 work in this project will be noticed in the small group of Cannon Fodder fans.

@endnode

@node "Opis" "Description"
@{B}@{FG Highlight}@{BG Shadow} Description                                                                  @{FG Text}@{BG Background}@{UB}
@{B}______________________________________________________________________________@{UB}
 Cannon Fodder New Campaign consists of 72 completly new maps grouped in 24
 missions. Phases system is the same like in old good Cannon Fodder. Besides
 maps you will notice new mission titles, soldiers, and small changes in
 graphics. Game engine is unchanged though.

 Every map can be completed. Maps were tested by testers and author.

@endnode



