@node "Wymagania" "Requirements"
@{B}@{FG Highlight}@{BG Shadow} Requirements                                                                 @{FG Text}@{BG Background}@{UB}
@{B}______________________________________________________________________________@{UB}
 - AmigaOS 2.0 up to 3.9
 - Cannon Fodder game (english, disk version)
 - WHDLoad package
 - Installer, XFDMaster, gpatch

 In addition we recommend:

 - CPU 68020 or better
 - Some Fast RAM (required by PRELOAD option)
 - Colour monitor
 - Audio ampfiler
 - Good mouse (important!)
@endnode



